reviewText: Love all of the Octopus series.  My husband and I make sure to time to watch an episode every afternoon!

This series is loaded with suspense, an excellent story line, plenty of mystery, and surprizing plots.  Yes, the music may be a bit lame occasionally and the speech fast enough to have to stop and play back the subtitles, but, it is outstanding!

I order all 10 seasons, because I have seen the first 6 in Europe. About the movie - an excellent and real story about Mafia in Italy/US. About the product (this and all others) - outstanding quality for years, very fast delivery, all in excellent condition as described. Highly recommend the sellers from CA and TX from which I purchase all discs. Very, very satisfied. It was great deal to me. Best regards.
J'ai reu ce dvd en temps et en heure, trs bien. je suis donc trs satisfait, que dire de plus?
